---
title: Archive
---

%h1 All Articles
- articles_by_year.each do |year, items|
    - if year != Date.today.year
        %h2= year
    %ul.article
        - items.each do |item|
            %li
                %a(href="#{route_path(item)}" title="#{item[:title]}")
                    = item[:title]
                %span.alternate &mdash; #{pretty_time(item[:created_at])}

